</p>
<p>resolution on maternal mortality in Africa (2008); and European Parliament, resolution on maternal 
mortality ahead of the UN High-level Event, 25 September &#8211; review of the Millennium Development 
Goals (2008). 
</p>
<p> 
</p>
<p>25
