(E/C.12/1/Add.80), 2002, para. 23; CRC concluding observations: Democratic People&#8217;s Republic of 
Korea (CRC/C/15/Add.239), para. 50; Ukraine (CRC/C/15/Add.151), para. 57. 
</p>
